Todos application.

An experiment to find out how complex it is to built something like the SproutCore (http://guides.sproutcore.com/html_based.html) or Backbone (http://documentcloud.github.com/backbone/examples/todos/index.html) Todo Demo with plain jQuery, jquery-datalink, handlebars and some basic glue code.


